            , were indicted for that they <rs id="t17800913-70-off409" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17800913-70-off409" type="offenceCategory" value="violentTheft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17800913-70-off409" type="offenceSubcategory" value="highwayRobbery"></interp>
               in the king's highway in and upon 
                     
                        <persName id="t17800913-70-victim742" type="victimName">
                           Marian 
                           De Rollo
                        <interp inst="t17800913-70-victim742" type="surname" value="De Rollo"></interp>
